<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="ida98bd435-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2021—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/117/81/s1043/1">Pub. L. 117–81, § 1043(1)</ref>, substituted “concerned” for “of a military department”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsec. (b)(1)(D). <ref href="/us/pl/117/81/s1043/2">Pub. L. 117–81, § 1043(2)</ref>, added subpar. (D).</p>
